{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","title":"setEmails:completion:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings."}]}],"name":"emails"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Block called when the operation completes.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setEmails:"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server registration completes."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Use this for confirmation UI or to chain dependent operations."}]},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import emails from third-party login with confirmation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class SocialLoginHandler {","","    func handleGoogleSignIn(_ user: GIDGoogleUser) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        \/\/ Primary email from Google","        if let email = user.profile?.email {","            emails.append(email)","        }","","        \/\/ Additional emails from Google profile if available","        if let additionalEmails = user.profile?.additionalEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: additionalEmails)","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Analytics.track(\"email_sync_failed\", properties: [","                    \"provider\": \"google\",","                    \"email_count\": emails.count,","                    \"error\": error.localizedDescription","                ])","                return","            }","","            Analytics.track(\"email_sync_success\", properties: [","                \"provider\": \"google\",","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            \/\/ Set user ID from Google","            Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.userID ?? \"\")","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:completion:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:completion:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"setEmails:completion:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:completion:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers multiple email addresses with completion handler."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:completion:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol","title":"PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}